/// Validation Helpers
///
/// Package name and version validation rules.
///
/// Functions defined in main.fg:
///
///   is_valid_package_name(name: string) -> bool
///     Rules:
///     - Must not be empty
///     - Must be <= 64 characters
///     - Must start with a letter or underscore
///     Returns false if any rule fails.
///
///   is_valid_version(version: string) -> bool
///     Rules:
///     - Must not be empty
///     - Must contain at least one dot (basic semver check)
///     Returns false if any rule fails.
///
/// Future validation could include:
///   - Full semver parsing (MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH)
///   - Package name character whitelist (alphanumeric, dash, underscore)
///   - Reserved name checking (std, forge, core, etc.)
///   - Version ordering / comparison
